Why do we need such luxurious things to prove our worth in this world?

60
00:06:56,712 --> 00:07:03,595
We force ourselves to make sure our phones are our newest models, our clothes are just off the runway, and our homes are of most extreme size and value.

61
00:07:04,195 --> 00:07:07,236
We constantly feel the need to compare ourselves to people around us.

62
00:07:07,936 --> 00:07:11,718
We are obsessed with the latest of trends, such as what did Kim Kardashian wear to the party?

63
00:07:12,422 --> 00:07:13,543
