73
00:07:56,461 --> 00:08:01,867
But because they are homeless, you choose to place them in a negative way without thinking about them as a person like yourself.

74
00:08:02,932 --> 00:08:08,914
them as a person in the sense of where they came from, who raised them, what are their goals in life, do they have children, do they have a spouse.

75
00:08:09,694 --> 00:08:14,615
