76
00:08:15,476 --> 00:08:20,777
For example, when a new neighbor moves in, you don't assume they are lazy or a drug addict, you assume they are just like yourself.

77
00:08:21,377 --> 00:08:27,199
Yet when you see a man asleep in an alleyway in Boston, you suddenly place negative terms on him such as criminal slob and trash.

78
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:29,900
Why must us as humans think like this?

79
00:08:30,361 --> 00:08:32,762
That person is just like you, whether you like it or not.

80
